#This section assesses the mandatory induction criteria
---
mandatory: True
question: Induction
subquestion: | 
  The next section asks you to briefly describe what steps were
  taken to induct you onto the job site.
  
  Inductions are a requirement before commencing work onsite.
  Please complete your answer.
buttons:
    - continue: continue
---
question: |
  What date were you inducted?
fields:
  - induction date: target_variable
    datatype: date
---
mandatory: True
question: |
  How were you inducted to site?.
fields:
  - Induction description: target_variable
    help: |
      This can be a brief description of the induction process
      meeting, saftey demo etc
    datatype: area
---
